<plot>Ephraim, a blind man, has been looking for the truth all his life: Why did his real parents give him up for adoption? Ephraim is not a normal blind man. He has the ability to touch people to feel their deepest secrets or touch photographs and see what was going on at that moment. One day his parents' lawyer visits him bringing some good and bad news but will he bring him the truth?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?179810</url></doc>
